response.overview: EVOLVE 134 took place at the Logan Square Auditorium in Chicago, Illinois. Matches featured • ZERO1 USA Heavyweight Title Match:  Jake Parnell (c) vs. Brubaker  • The Besties In The World (Davey Vega & Mat Fitchett) vs. The Skulk (Adrian Alanis & Liam Gray) vs. The Unwanted (Joe Gacy & Sean Maluta)  • Anthony Gutierrez vs. Jimmy Karryt  • No Holds Barred Match:  Anthony Henry vs. Arturo Ruas  • Freestyle Match:  GPA vs. Craig Mitchell vs. Stephen Wolf vs. Brandon Taggart vs. Karam vs. Noah Gray • EVOLVE Tag Team Title Match:  AR Fox & Leon Ruff (c) vs. Curt Stallion & Matt Riddle • Anthony Greene (w/Brandi Lauren) vs. PACO • Kendo Sticks Are Legal Match:  Brandi Lauren vs. Shotzi Blackheart • EVOLVE Title Triple Threat Match:  Austin Theory (c) vs. JD Drake vs. Josh Briggs • WWE Cruiserweight Title Match:  Drew Gulak (c) vs. Kushida.
response.title: EVOLVE 134
